short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This extension will integrate the Aorder admin onto the Tellix back office

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Use this extension to add a launcher button of Aorder on your Tellix backoffice, allowing you to use and manage your Aorder shop and admin without needing you to leave the backoffice.
